irst to learn how a plane operates before adding weapons. The game for all its detail is not without controversy as to realism. The energy rules and the claim that some aspects of the game are based on educated guesses because of the info on some planes being top secret, have caused this feeling of fudging.\n\nAll in all one of SPI's most ambitious projects. There is also an expansion - Air War Update Kit.\n\n	120	120	120	1977	2	4	2	David C. Isby
