a: 1" = 4 miles \nUnits: Battalion to Brigade\n\nGame Inventory:\nOne 22" X 34" mapsheet\nTwo countersheets (352 5/8" counters)\nOne 16 page rules booklet\nFive Scenario Cards\nOne Player Aid Card\nFour 10 sided sided die\n\n	300	300	300	1999	2	2	2	Ray Freeman
