ght. There are special overlays for Port Arthur and Chemulpo, so players can use the actual terrain of these key coastal zones.\n\nThe original 1999 game included:\n\n210 Counters\n    One 25"x30" strategic map\n    One 25"x25" tactical map\n    16 page Rulebook\n    12 page Scenario book\n\nThe game is being re-implemented in 2013 as Great War at Sea: Russo-Japanese War with a revised map, updated counters, new scenario book and new box.\n\n	30	30	30	1999	2	4	2	Michael Bennighof
